Class BinaryTree<K extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<K>,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • BinaryTree<K,E>

  • public class BinaryTree<K extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable<K>,E>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as a BinaryTree. It will store information, an element, based on a comparable Number (it's key).
    Author:
    Craig Lombardo
